  "text": "We start with a very brief overview of the full expert system and the task it performs. (For a more detailed description of the passive sonar understanding problem and an expert system architecture suited to this problem, see [CITATION_1] .) We then describe the structure of the event detection rules (the tuning of which will be the focus of the paper). Finally, we discuss the necessity of learning mechanisms to allow the expert system to improve with experience.",
